In re Resignation of Nash.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Nash (1993), 68 Ohio St.3d 1207.]

(No. 93-2365 Submitted December 15, 1993 Decided December 16, 1993.)

On Affidavit of Resignation.

The resignation of Mary Godfrey Nash of Hamilton, Ohio, as an attorney, Registration No. 0012559, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
